mydf %>%
  group_by(seriescol) %>%
  e_chart(xcol) %>%
  e_line(ycol, endLabel = list(show = TRUE, formatter = "{a}"))

  e_chart(xcol) %>%
  e_line(ycol, endLabel = list(show = TRUE, formatter = "{a}", color = "inherit")) %>%
